txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Leathery fur from the beasts in the lands surrounding the Ranger-outpost at Tinnudir. You are to deliver the items to the Ranger Astiul at the outpost on the shores of Lake Evendim.
'I will see that these are given to those who can put them to good use.'
'Though supplies are not diminished too much, thus far, it is good to prepare for the future. We could use skins and furs from the beasts surrounding this land.'
Wardens of Ann√∫minas Task: Leathery Fur
Tinnudir, a Ranger-outpost on the eastern shore of Lake Evendim, is home to the Rangers of Evendim. There, at the outpost, a Ranger named Astiul awaits the return of leathery fur.
Deliver the leathery fur to Astiul at the Ranger-outpost of Tinnudir
You have been tasked with collecting leathery fur from the beasts surrounding Tinnudir. You are to deliver the items to the Ranger Astiul within the lakeside outpost.
Wanted: Leathery fur from the beasts in the lands surrounding the Ranger-outpost at Tinnudir.
